# This repo lives inside the live ~/.copilot state directory.
# Ignore everything by default so caches, logs, DBs, browser profiles,
# OAuth state, chat history, and local secrets never show up accidentally.
*

# Existing tracked files still report modifications normally.
# New files must be added intentionally with `git add -f <path>`.
!.gitignore
!README.md
!copilot-instructions.md
!mcp-config.example.json
!hooks/
!hooks/**
!instructions/
!instructions/**
!skills/
!skills/**
!agents/
!agents/**
!plugin.json
!plugins/
!plugins/**
!.mcp.json
!.github/
!.github/**

# Generated or sensitive skill/runtime state.
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
*.log
**/*.log
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
outputs/
**/outputs/
profile/
**/profile/
skills/google-search copy/
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal

# Local config/state with secrets or machine-specific values.
mcp-config.json
mcp-oauth-config/
*.bak
*.enc
